\c 3
\s USolomoni uthatha indodakazi kaFaro
\p
\v 1 USolomoni wasehlangana ngomtshado loFaro inkosi yeGibhithe, wathatha indodakazi kaFaro\x + 7.8. 9.16,24. 11.1. 2 Lan. 8.11.\x*, wayiletha emzini kaDavida\x + 2.10.\x* waze waqeda ukwakha indlu yakhe\x + 7.1.\x* lendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* lomduli weJerusalema ozingelezeleyo\x + 9.15,19.\x*.
\v 2 Kube kanti abantu babenikela umhlatshelo endaweni eziphakemeyo, ngoba kwakungakhelwanga ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* indlu kwaze kwaba yilezonsuku.
\v 3 USolomoni wayithanda-ke iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Dute. 30.16,20. Hlab. 31.23. Dute. 6.5.\x*, ehamba ezimisweni zikaDavida uyise\x + 3.6,14.\x*; kube kanti wanikela umhlatshelo watshisa impepha endaweni eziphakemeyo.
\v 4 Inkosi yasisiya eGibeyoni ukuhlaba khona\x + Josh. 9.3.\x*, ngoba leyo yayiyindawo ephakemeyo\x + 1 Sam. 9.12.\x* enkulu\x + 1 Lan. 16.39. 21.29. 2 Lan. 1.3,6,13.\x*. Iminikelo yokutshiswa eyinkulungwane uSolomoni wayinikela phezu kwalelolathi\x + 2 Lan. 1.6.\x*.
\s USolomoni ucela ingqondo yokuqedisisa
\p
\v 5 EGibeyoni iN\nd kosi\nd* yabonakala kuSolomoni\x + 9.2. 11.9. 2 Lan. 1.7-12.\x* ephutsheni ebusuku. UNkulunkulu wathi: Cela engingakunika khona\x + Nani 12.6.\x*.
\v 6 USolomoni wasesithi: Wena wenzele inceku yakho uDavida ubaba umusa omkhulu, njengokuhamba kwakhe phambi kwakho eqinisweni lekulungeni lebuqothweni benhliziyo kuwe; wamgcinela lo umusa omkhulu\x + 2.4. 9.4. Hlab. 15.2.\x* ukuthi wamnika indodana ehlezi esihlalweni sakhe sobukhosi njengalamuhla\x + 1.48.\x*.
\v 7 Ngakho-ke, N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wami, wena wenzile inceku yakho yaba yinkosi esikhundleni sikaDavida ubaba\x + 1 Lan. 28.5.\x*; ngingumntwanyana nje\x + 11.17. 1 Lan. 29.1. 2 Kho. 2.23.\x*, angikwazi ukuphuma lokungena\x + Nani 27.17.\x*.
\v 8 Lenceku yakho iphakathi kwabantu bakho obakhethileyo, abantu abanengi\x + Dute. 7.6.\x*, abangelakubalwa labangelakunaniswa ngobunengi\x + Gen. 13.16. 15.5.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho nika inceku yakho inhliziyo eqedisisayo\x + Jak. 1.5. Zaga 2.3-9.\x* ukwahlulela abantu bakho\x + Hlab. 72.1,2.\x*, ukuze ngehlukanise phakathi kokuhle lokubi; ngoba ngubani olamandla ukwahlulela lesisizwe sakho esikhulu\x + Isa. 7.15. Heb. 5.14.\x*?
\v 10 Laloludaba lwaba luhle emehlweni eNkosi ukuthi uSolomoni ucele lolulutho\x + Gen. 45.16.\x*.
\v 11 UNkulunkulu wasesithi kuye: Ngenxa yokuthi ucele lolulutho, ungazicelelanga insuku ezinengi, ungazicelelanga inotho, ungacelanga umphefumulo wezitha zakho, kodwa uzicelele ukuqedisisa ukuzwa ukwahlulela,
\v 12 khangela, sengenze njengamazwi akho\x + 1 Joha. 5.14,15.\x*. Khangela, ngikunike inhliziyo ehlakaniphileyo leqedisisayo, ukuthi kungabi khona onjengawe ngaphambi kwakho, lemva kwakho kungaveli onjengawe\x + 4.29-31. 5.12. 10.24. Tshu. 1.16.\x*.
\v 13 Futhi longakucelanga ngikunikile\x + Mat. 6.33.\x*, ngitsho inotho lodumo, ukuze kungabi khona umuntu onjengawe emakhosini zonke izinsuku zakho\x + 4.21-24. 10.23,25. Zaga 3.16.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo uba uzahamba endleleni zami, ukugcina izimiso zami lemilayo yami njengoDavida uyihlo wahamba\x + 15.5.\x*, ngizakwelula insuku zakho\x + Hlab. 91.16. Zaga 3.2.\x*.
\v 15 USolomoni wasephaphama; khangela-ke kwakuliphupho\x + Gen. 41.7.\x*. Wasesiza eJerusalema, wema phambi komtshokotsho wesivumelwano seNkosi\x + 2 Sam. 6.17. 2 Lan. 1.4.\x*, wanikela iminikelo yokutshiswa, wanikela iminikelo yokuthula, wenzela inceku zakhe zonke idili\x + 8.65. Gen. 40.20. Esta 1.3.2.18. Dan. 5.1. Mark. 6.21.\x*.
\s Ukuhlakanipha kukaSolomoni ekwahluleleni
\p
\v 16 Ngalesosikhathi kwafika abesifazana ababili, amawule, enkosini, bema phambi kwayo\x + Nani 27.2.\x*.
\v 17 Omunye owesifazana wasesithi: Hawu nkosi yami, mina lalumfazi sihlala ndlunye; ngasengibeletha ngilaye endlini.
\v 18 Kwasekusithi ngosuku lwesithathu ngibelethile, laye lumfazi wabeletha; njalo sasindawonye, kungekho owemzini kanye lathi endlini, ngaphandle kwethu sobabili endlini.
\v 19 Umntwana walumfazi wasesifa ebusuku, ngoba walala phezu kwakhe.
\v 20 Wasevuka phakathi kobusuku, wathatha indodana yami eceleni kwami, incekukazi yakho isalele, wayilalisa esifubeni sakhe, lomntanakhe ofileyo wamlalisa esifubeni sami.
\v 21 Lapho ngivuka ekuseni ukumunyisa umntanami, khangela-ke wayesefile; sengimkhangelisisa ekuseni, khangela-ke, kwakungeyisuye umntanami engamzalayo.
\v 22 Kodwa lowo omunye owesifazana wathi: Hatshi, kodwa indodana yami ngephilayo, lendodana yakho ngefileyo. Lalowo wathi: Hatshi, kodwa indodana yakho ngefileyo, lendodana yami ngephilayo. Batsho njalo phambi kwenkosi.
\v 23 Inkosi yasisithi: Lo uthi: Le yindodana yami ephilayo, lendodana yakho ngefileyo; lomunye uthi: Hatshi, kodwa indodana yakho ngefileyo, lendodana yami ngephilayo.
\v 24 Inkosi yasisithi: Ngithathelani inkemba. Basebeyiletha inkemba phambi kwenkosi.
\v 25 Inkosi yasisithi: Dabulani kabili umntwana ophilayo, linike omunye ingxenye, lomunye ingxenye.
\v 26 Owesifazana okwakungowakhe umntwana ophilayo wakhuluma enkosini, ngoba imibilini yakhe yavutha ngendodana yakhe, wathi: Hawu nkosi yami, mnikeni yena umntwana ophilayo, lingambulali loba kunjani. Kodwa omunye wathi: Kangabi ngowami kumbe ngowakho, dabulani.
\v 27 Inkosi yasiphendula yathi: Nikani yena umntwana ophilayo, lingambulali loba kunjani; nguye unina.
\v 28 UIsrayeli wonke wasesizwa isahlulelo inkosi eyayisahlulele, besaba phambi kwenkosi, ngoba babona ukuthi inhlakanipho kaNkulunkulu yayikuye ukwenza isahlulelo\x + 3.9,11,12.\x*.